rows.label: qev093203_MSG0010
rows.name:
Hey. So we did some legwork and
picked up the ingredients.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093203_MSG0020
rows.name: Y-you really went and fetched them all for us?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093203_MSG0030
rows.name:
C'mon. Give us what we want.
My stomach's turning inside out...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093203_MSG0040
rows.name: Oh, sure—right away![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093203_MSG0050
rows.name: U-uhh...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093203_MSG0060
rows.name: Ah, the man of the hour. You kept us waiting![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093203_MSG0070
rows.name:
N-no, that's not—
The thing is...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093203_MSG0080
rows.name: Sir...we're completely out of pepperoni.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093203_MSG0090
rows.name: ...Huh?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093203_MSG0100
rows.name:
Did I hear that right? You're OUT?
Of pepperoni?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093203_MSG0110
rows.name: PEPPERONI? The God-king of toppings...?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093203_MSG0120
rows.name: G-uuhhh...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093203_MSG0130
rows.name:
Good sir, you serve pizza.
Surely you must know the divine nature of pepperoni![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093203_MSG0140
rows.name:
In fact, if you knew you were out,
why didn't you think to put it on the list?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093203_MSG0150
rows.name: I—I'm sorry![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093203_MSG0160
rows.name:
Ah, though if you'd like a veggie pizza,
we can get that to you right away![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093203_MSG0170
rows.name:
Dude. Are you trying to upset me here?
Do you also eat your burgers without the patty?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093203_MSG0180
rows.name: C-certainly not! I'll go get the Mediators—[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093203_MSG0190
rows.name:
Forget it—we'll sort this out ourselves.
Point us to the pepperoni.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093203_MSG0200
rows.name:
Ah, we use suid meat for our pepperoni,
and we can make it in-house, nice and fresh while you wait![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093203_MSG0210
rows.name:
Suid... That's those pig-like indigens, right?
Where are they?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093203_MSG0220
rows.name:
Err... Primordia. There should be a herd of them
outside NLA—it's not far at all.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093203_MSG0230
rows.name: If you can get a hold of the suid meat for us...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093203_MSG0240
rows.name: You heard the man. Let's get hunting![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093203_MSG0250
rows.name: I'm so sorry about all this.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093203_MSG0260
rows.name: Save it. You just make sure that oven's preheated.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093203_MSG0270
rows.name:
The moment we get back, you bake
that pizza lickedy-split! Got it?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093203_MSG0280
rows.name: S-SIR, YES, SIR![ST:wait ]
